<doc id="335188" wikidata="Q2643634" url="?curid=335188" title="Slender slider">
<text>The slender slider (Pletholax gracilis) is a species of lizard in the family Pygopodidae.

==Geographic range==
&quot;Pletholax gracilis&quot; is endemic to coastal areas of southwestern Australia.

==References==</text><links>
